Package: fixrmdsubmissions
Title: Automatically Fix Common Issues in Student R Markdown Submissions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("StÃ©fan", "Janse van Rensburg", , "stefanj@mandala.ac.za", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0749-2277"))
Description: Automatically repairs common technical issues in student R Markdown
    submissions so they can be knit reliably. Sequentially evaluates code chunks,
    adds 'eval = FALSE' to failing chunks, and intelligently fixes bare file paths
    to use the 'here' package. Designed for instructors who need to process hundreds
    of submissions with minimal manual intervention.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
